---
title: Hearty Beef & Basil Pesto Fusilli with Apple Salad & Parmesan
description: In this dish, we've teamed rich basil pesto with a silky cream-based sauce, then followed it up with tender beef mince for a quick meal that looks and smells every bit as good as it tastes.

*Unfortunately, this
week's penne was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with fusilli.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
